<BaseLayout
  title="Lead Generation Strategies for Service Businesses | Sushvin AI Labs"
  description="Lead generation strategies for service businesses: practical tactics to attract and convert local customers."
  keywords="lead generation, local business leads, Mysuru marketing, service business growth"
>
  <Header />

  <div class="container">
    <article>
      <h1>Lead Generation Strategies for Service Businesses</h1>
      <p class="article-meta">
        <strong>Published:</strong> November 24, 2025 •
        <strong>Reading Time:</strong> 7 minutes
      </p>

      <p>
        Practical tactics to attract, capture, and convert local leads for
        clinics, salons, coaching centers, and other service businesses.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Optimize Local Listings</h2>
      <p>
        Complete your Google Business Profile with accurate details, services,
        photos, and regular posts. Encourage satisfied customers to leave
        reviews to improve visibility for “near me” searches.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Capture Leads on Your Website</h2>
      <p>
        Use short contact forms, chat widgets, and WhatsApp buttons to capture
        visitor intent with minimal friction. The easier it is to contact you,
        the higher your conversion rate.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Nurture Leads with Automated Sequences</h2>
      <p>
        Most leads don’t convert on the first interaction. Automate follow-ups
        using WhatsApp, SMS, or email to remind, educate, and build trust until
        the customer is ready to book.
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Example:</strong>
        A salon increased conversions by 30% after adding an automated WhatsApp
        follow-up offering a 10% first-booking coupon.
      </div>

      <h2>4. Use Clear Calls-to-Action</h2>
      <p>
        Every page should guide visitors toward one primary action — booking a
        call, starting a WhatsApp chat, or submitting a form. Avoid clutter and
        confusion.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Track and Improve</h2>
      <p>
        Measure where leads come from, how fast you respond, and which channels
        convert best. Continuous optimization turns average lead flow into
        predictable growth.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Want More Leads?</h3>
        <p>
          Sushvin AI Labs builds lead funnels and WhatsApp automations that
          actually convert visitors into paying customers.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Talk to an Expert
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>